        "body": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since 2018, our small California studio has crafted handmade gemstone and pearl bracelets from materials chosen for their natural beauty — not factory uniformity. Every pearl, every stone, every silver detail is selected by hand and assembled one piece at a time. We believe imperfections are what make natural jewelry meaningful: the irregular shape of a baroque pearl, the color shift inside an amethyst, the unrepeatable banding of an agate. These aren't flaws — they're signatures of something real.</p>",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "max_width": "narrow",
            "alignment": "center",
