    "materials_deep": {
      "type": "kinsoul-materials-deep",
      "blocks": {
        "pearls": {
          "type": "material_profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/a462ae552c112aea4711b6de9b734fb0.png",
            "label": "Material 01",
            "title": "Natural Pearls",
            "body": "<p>Every Kinsoul bracelet featuring pearls uses genuine baroque or freshwater pearls — never imitation, never coated glass. Baroque pearls are valued precisely for their irregular, organic forms: no two share the same shape, size, or surface texture. This natural variation is what gives each piece its character.</p><p>Freshwater pearls develop their luster slowly, layer by layer, inside a living mollusk. The result is a soft, warm glow that synthetic alternatives cannot replicate. We select pearls for their organic beauty — the gentle ridges, the way light moves across an imperfect surface. Our collection includes baroque centerpiece pearls, freshwater rice pearls, and pearl silver bars, each chosen to complement the stones they sit beside.</p><p>A care note: pearls thrive when worn close to your skin. The natural oils from your body help maintain their luminosity over time. Put them on last, take them off first — and they'll age beautifully.</p>",
            "anchor": "pearls",
            "found_in_label": "Found In",
            "product_1_url": "/products/persian-red-agate-pearl-sterling-silver-bracelet",
            "product_1_name": "Ember",
            "product_2_url": "/products/freeform-amethyst-bracelet-with-freshwater-pearls",
            "product_2_name": "Serenity",
            "product_3_url": "/products/aura-balance-bracelet-baroque-pearl-crystal-mixed-gemstones",
            "product_3_name": "Aura",
            "product_4_url": "/products/mozhu-persian-agate-baroque-pearl-bracelet",
            "product_4_name": "Obsidian",
            "product_5_url": "/products/moqiao-black-agate-rutilated-quartz-pearl-bracelet",
            "product_5_name": "Terra"
          }
        },
        "gemstones": {
          "type": "material_profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/ac7c941f089f2cc721d9bd5bece2d52b.png",
            "label": "Material 02",
            "title": "Hand-Selected Gemstones",
            "body": "<p>Our bracelets feature over ten varieties of natural gemstones: amethyst, Persian red agate, black agate, Persian banded agate, Brazilian citrine, clear quartz, rutilated quartz, tiger's eye, lapis lazuli, amazonite, and red jasper. Every stone is hand-cut and minimally polished to preserve its natural texture, color variation, and internal inclusions.</p><p>We don't chase uniformity. A piece of amethyst might range from soft lavender to deep violet. Banded agate reveals geological layers formed over millions of years — each stripe a fingerprint of slow, patient mineral deposits. Rutilated quartz contains silver needle-like inclusions that look like captured light. These natural characteristics are what make each bracelet genuinely one of a kind.</p><p>In many cultures, these stones carry quiet traditions: amethyst for calm and clarity, red agate for confidence and vitality, lapis lazuli for wisdom, citrine for optimism. We share these traditions honestly — not as magic, but as the intention behind choosing something meaningful from the earth.</p>",
            "anchor": "gemstones",
            "found_in_label": "Found In All Six Bracelets",
            "product_1_url": "/products/persian-red-agate-pearl-sterling-silver-bracelet",
            "product_1_name": "Ember",
            "product_2_url": "/products/freeform-amethyst-bracelet-with-freshwater-pearls",
            "product_2_name": "Serenity",
            "product_3_url": "/products/aura-balance-bracelet-baroque-pearl-crystal-mixed-gemstones",
            "product_3_name": "Aura",
            "product_4_url": "/products/mozhu-persian-agate-baroque-pearl-bracelet",
            "product_4_name": "Obsidian",
            "product_5_url": "/products/moqiao-black-agate-rutilated-quartz-pearl-bracelet",
            "product_5_name": "Terra"
          }
        },
        "silver": {
          "type": "material_profile",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/logo.jpg",
            "label": "Material 03",
            "title": "S925 Sterling Silver",
            "body": "<p>All metal components in our bracelets — the maker's mark bar, spacers, and accent details — are crafted from S925 sterling silver, meaning 92.5% pure silver alloyed for strength and durability. Each piece is hand-finished for a smooth feel against the skin.</p><p>Some pieces, like the Terra bracelet, feature spacers with an intentional antique finish that echoes the warm, earthy tones of the stones. Over time, sterling silver may develop a natural patina — a soft darkening that many wearers appreciate as part of the piece's evolution. A gentle polish with a soft cloth restores its original luster whenever you prefer.</p><p>The small S925 bar on every bracelet carries our Kinsoul mark — a subtle signature that identifies each piece as genuine, without overpowering the stones and pearls it sits beside.</p>",
            "anchor": "silver",
            "found_in_label": "Found In All Six Bracelets",
            "product_1_url": "/products/persian-red-agate-pearl-sterling-silver-bracelet",
